489
00:50:13,978 --> 00:50:15,172
Got it!

490
00:50:21,352 --> 00:50:24,048
You've already gone through this, right?
You saw...

491
00:50:24,922 --> 00:50:26,257
Well, you can tell that that's
how she painted it.

