01:20:19,048 --> 01:20:21,346
It's lovely to see you, Temple.

827
01:20:22,017 --> 01:20:25,077
- Bye.
- Merry Christmas.

828
01:20:26,522 --> 01:20:27,921
Merry Christmas!

829
01:20:29,758 --> 01:20:32,352
