878
01:25:10,038 --> 01:25:12,408
This is very clever.
How did you come up with this?

879
01:25:12,508 --> 01:25:13,909
I just see things and put them together.

880
01:25:14,009 --> 01:25:15,310
- So how long will it take you to...
